---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="Contact" description="Contact FlowHat Blog for inquiries, corrections, advertising, and privacy requests">
	<h1>Contact FlowHat Blog</h1>
	<p>
		For questions about FlowHat Blog, corrections, advertising inquiries, sponsorship discussions, or
		privacy-related requests, contact the site by email.
	</p>

	<h2>Email</h2>
	<p>
		<a href="mailto:flowhatt@gmail.com">flowhatt@gmail.com</a>
	</p>

	<h2>Corrections and updates</h2>
	<p>
		If an article contains an error, outdated information, or a broken source link, please include the
		article URL and a short explanation of the issue. FlowHat Blog may update articles when products,
		documentation, or source material changes.
	</p>

	<h2>Advertising and sponsorship</h2>
	<p>
		Advertising, sponsorship, and partnership inquiries can be sent to the same email address. Sponsored
		content, if accepted, should be clearly identified and should not override the site's editorial view.
		See the <a href="/disclosure/">Disclosure</a> page for more detail.
	</p>

	<h2>Privacy requests</h2>
	<p>
		For privacy-related questions about analytics, advertising, cookies, or data practices, include
		"Privacy request" in the email subject when possible. See the <a href="/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a>
		for the site's current privacy information.
	</p>
</PageLayout>
